vn.map4d.map4dsdk.camera

Class MFCameraUpdateFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • vn.map4d.map4dsdk.camera.MFCameraUpdateFactory

  • public final class MFCameraUpdateFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A class containing methods for creating MFCameraUpdate objects that change a map's camera.

      • newLatLng

        public static MFCameraUpdate newLatLng(LatLng latLng)
        Returns a CameraUpdate that moves the center of the screen to a latitude and longitude specified by a LatLng object. This centers the camera on the LatLng object.
        Parameters:
        latLng - Target location to change to
        Returns:
        CameraUpdate Final Camera Position

      • newLatLngBounds

        public static MFCameraUpdate newLatLngBounds(LatLngBounds bounds,
                                             int padding)
        Returns a CameraUpdate that transforms the camera such that the specified latitude/longitude bounds are centered on screen at the greatest possible zoom level. You can specify padding, in order to inset the bounding box from the map view's edges. The returned CameraUpdate has a bearing of 0 and a tilt of 0.
        Parameters:
        bounds - Bounds to match Camera position with
        padding - Padding for Left, Top, Right, Bottom added to the bounds
        Returns:
        CameraUpdate Final Camera Position

      • newLatLngBounds

        public static MFCameraUpdate newLatLngBounds(LatLngBounds bounds,
                                             int paddingLeft,
                                             int paddingTop,
                                             int paddingRight,
                                             int paddingBottom)
        Returns a CameraUpdate that transforms the camera such that the specified latitude/longitude bounds are centered on screen at the greatest possible zoom level. You can specify padding, in order to inset the bounding box from the map view's edges. The returned CameraUpdate has a bearing of 0 and a tilt of 0.
        Parameters:
        bounds - Bounds to match Camera position with
        paddingLeft - PaddingLeft added to the bounds
        paddingTop - PaddingTop added to the bounds
        paddingRight - PaddingRight added to the bounds
        paddingBottom - PaddingBottom added to the bounds
        Returns:
        CameraUpdate Final Camera Position

      • zoomIn

        public static MFCameraUpdate zoomIn()
        Returns a MFCameraUpdate that zooms in on the map by moving the viewpoint's height closer to the Earth's surface. The zoom increment is 1.0.

        a MFCameraUpdate containing the transformation.
